-open-day-seven-2024-09-01/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示8月份中国新建住宅价格涨幅放缓</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-new-home-prices-rise-more-slowly-august-survey-shows-2024-09-01/</link><description>当地政策制定者一直在努力促进销售或增加流动性。</description><pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 02:11:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-new-home-prices-rise-more-slowly-august-survey-shows-2024-09-01/</guid></item><item><title>日本抗议中国一周内第二次入侵领土</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navy-survey-ship-entered-japanese-waters-japans-defence-ministry-says-2024-08-31/</link><description>日本一艘海军调查船周六进入日本海域，这是中国军队不到一周内第二次入侵日本领土，日本就此向中国提出抗议。</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 08:30:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-navy-survey-ship-entered-japanese-waters-japans-defence-ministry-says-2024-08-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国、菲律宾互相指责对方在南海撞船</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-coast-guard-says-philippine-ship-rammed-chinese-vessel-south-china-sea-2024-08-31/</link><description>周六，菲律宾和中国相互指责在南海有争议的水域故意撞击海岸警卫队船只，这是这条重要水道上一系列不断升级的冲突中的最新一起。</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 08:09:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-coast-guard-says-philippine-ship-rammed-chinese-vessel-south-china-sea-2024-08-31/</guid></item><item><title>联合国关于中国侵权行为的报告两年后，挫败感加深</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/frustration-deepens-two-years-after-un-report-china-abuses-2024-08-31/</link><description>中国坚决否认新疆存在任何侵权行为。</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 06:06:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/frustration-deepens-two-years-after-un-report-china-abuses-2024-08-31/</guid></item><item><title>中国疲软的工厂PMI增加了刺激消费的压力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinas-august-manufacturing-activity-falls-fourth-month-2024-08-31/</link><description>周六的一项官方调查显示，由于工厂